### Writing guidance

Describe changes from the user's or affected role's perspective. Reference vocabulary terms exactly as defined above.

### Item template

```markdown
# BG-NNN: Title

Priority: P0 | P1 | P2 | P3
Status: Proposed
Theme: <!-- PRODUCT: Define your themes (e.g., Foundation, User Experience, API) -->
Spec: spec/<domain>.md > Section Name

## Why now
## What changes
## Acceptance criteria
## Out of scope
## Dependencies
## Notes
```

### Implementation Sections (appended by Change-Orchestrator)

```markdown
## Implementation Plan
## Task List
- [ ] Task one
- [ ] Task two
## Implementation Notes
## Tests
```

